Q: Complete the following line from the Hindu chant Pavamana Mantra:
Asato ma sadgamaya, tamaso ma \PYGZus{}\PYGZus{}\PYGZus{}\PYGZus{}\PYGZus{}\PYGZus{}\PYGZus{}\PYGZus{}.
 choice: varenyam
 choice: amritam gamaya
 choice: dhimahi
 choice: jyotirgamaya
A:

Choices: \PYGZsq{}jyotirgamaya\PYGZsq{} (\PYGZhy{}0.8), \PYGZsq{}amritam gamaya\PYGZsq{} (\PYGZhy{}2.5),
\PYGZsq{}varenyam\PYGZsq{} (\PYGZhy{}4.0), \PYGZsq{}dhimahi\PYGZsq{} (\PYGZhy{}5.6)
Target: \PYGZsq{}jyotirgamaya\PYGZsq{}


Q: When you sleep, which organ is more involved?
 choice: all of them
 choice: eye
 choice: brain
 choice: hand
